The paper discusses the security and privacy challenges in smart grid systems and proposes a solution that leverages trusted hardware SGX. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Cybersecurity (cs.CY).
